###  https://w3id.org/mqto
<https://w3id.org/mqto> rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ;
                        dcterms:creator <https://orcid.org/0000-0001-9521-8907> ;
                        dcterms:description "A generalised ontology for manufacturing quality troubleshooting, applicable across different manufacturing domains. Covers both the specified (schema-level) and actual (instance-level) layers of a manufacturing process, with a focus on root cause analysis, failure diagnosis, and countermeasure recommendation."@en .


###  https://w3id.org/mqto#nil
mqto:nil rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                  mqto:List ;
         rdfs:label "nil"@en .


